1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 (2... d6 3. Bc4 Bg4 4. Nc3 g6? 5. Nxe5!! Bxd1?? 6. Bxf7+ Ke7 7. Nd5#) 3. Bc4 d6?! (3... Nf6 4. Nc3 Nxe4 5. Nxe4 d5 6. Bd3 dxe4 7. Bxe4 $14) 4. Nc3 Bg4 5. h3 Bh5? (5... Bxf3 6. Qxf3 $14 { This doesn't lead to checkmate but white is slightly better. } 6... Nf6 7. O-O Nd4 8. Qd3) 6. Nxe5!! Bxd1?? 7. Bxf7+ Ke7 $7 8. Nd5# { This is a beautiful checkmate called legal mate } *
